quran[34]{c,v,t}:
  56,17,Yetufu ÂṀaleyhim veldanun muhalledune
  56,18,Biekvabin ve ebariyka ve keÂṀsin min maÂṀÄḟynin
  56,19,La yusaddaÂṀune ÂṀanha ve la yunzifune
  56,20,Ve fakihetin mimma yetehayyerune
