  56,22,Ve hurun ÂṀÄḟynun
  56,23,KeemsalilluÂṀluilmeknuni
  56,24,Cezaen bima kanu yaÂṀmelune
  56,25,La yesmeÂṀune fiyha laÄven ve la teÂṀsiymen
  56,26,ÄḞlla kÄḟylen selamen selamen
